==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Charmer
<hw>Charm"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
charms, or has power to charm; one who uses the power of enchantment; a
magician.</def> <rj><au>Deut. xviii. 11.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who delights and attracts the
affections.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Charmeress</ent>⟦br⟧
